- 'Actively making predictions' refers to models with a status of 'active' and prediction dates on or after '2023-01-01'; 
- Performance is measured by the 'accuracy' metric value; 
- 'Top 5 models' means the models with the lowest performance ranks.

- High performance metric value (> 0.8) indicates good model performance; 
- High data quality score (> 0.8) indicates reliable dataset; 
- Active integration status signifies that the model is currently being used and integrated into the system.
